    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_54",
      "heading": "2.  in  this Act,  unless  the  context  otherwise  requires—",
      "content": "2.  in  this Act,  unless  the  context  otherwise  requires—",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_55",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“child” includes a step-child and a child adopted by the recipient \nunder  any  written  law  relating  to  adoption;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_56",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“remembrance  allowance”  means  the  remembrance  allowance \ngranted  under  subsection  3(1);",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_57",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "6",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_58",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Laws  of  Malaysia",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_59",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Act  744",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_60",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“spouse” means the widow or widower of a deceased recipient \nwhose  marriage  is  recognized  in  Malaysia  as  a  valid  marriage \nunder  any  written  law,  religion  or  custom;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_61",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“recipient”  means  a  person  who  has  been  conferred  the \nDecoration;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_62",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“social  guarantor”  means  a  person  who  provides,  not  for  the \npurpose  of  making  profit,  any  of  the  following  guarantees:",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_63",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(a)  a guarantee for a loan, scholarship or grant for educational",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_64",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "or  research  purposes;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_65",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(b)  a  guarantee  for  a  hire-purchase  transaction  of  a  vehicle",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_66",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "for  personal  or  non-business  use;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_67",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(c)  a  guarantee  for  a  housing  loan  transaction  solely  for",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_68",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "personal  dwelling;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_69",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“Decoration” means the Decoration of Jasa Perkasa Persekutuan \nconferred  under  the  Statutes  of  Jasa  Perkasa  Persekutuan \n[G.N.  3152/60].",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_70",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Grant  of  remembrance  allowance",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_71",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "3.  (1)  There  may  be  granted  to  a  recipient  of  a  Decoration  a \nremembrance  allowance  of  one  thousand  ringgit  a  month,  and \nwhere  the  Decoration  is  conferred  on  such  recipient  more  than \nonce,  there  may  be  granted  to  him  a  separate  remembrance \nallowance  of  one  thousand  ringgit  a  month  in  respect  of  each \nDecoration  conferred  on  him.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_72",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2)  The  remembrance  allowance  shall  only  be  payable  to  a",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_73",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "recipient  who  is  still  living  at  the  commencement  of  this Act.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_74",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(3)  The  remembrance  allowance  shall  be  payable  in  arrear  no",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_75",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "earlier  than  the  end  of  each  month.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_76",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(4)  Where the Decoration is conferred before the commencement \nof this Act, the remembrance allowance shall be paid to the recipient, \nin  any  case,  commencing  with  the  month  of  the  commencement \nof  this Act.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_77",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(5)  Where  the  Decoration  is  conferred  on  or  after  the \ncommencement  of  this Act,  the  remembrance  allowance  shall  be \npaid  to  the  recipient  commencing  with  the  month  in  which  the",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_78",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Jasa  Perkasa  Persekutuan  (Remembrance  Allowance)",
      "section_number": null,
