      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_84",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(b)  if the recipient has been convicted for any offence by a",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_85",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "court  of  law  in  the  Federation;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_86",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(c)  if the recipient has been ordered by a court of law in the \nFederation  in  any  civil  action  to  pay  an  amount  which \nexceeds  two  thousand  ringgit;  or",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_87",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(d)  upon the cancellation or annulment of the conferment of \nthe  Decoration  in  accordance  with  section  Viii  of  the \nStatutes  of  Jasa  Perkasa  Persekutuan.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_88",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2)  No  remembrance  allowance  shall  be  paid  commencing—",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_89",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(a)  with the month in which the death of the recipient takes",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_90",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "place;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_91",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(b)  with  the  month  in  which  the  sentence  for  an  offence  is",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_92",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "imposed  on  the  recipient;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_93",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(c)  with the month in which the order referred to in paragraph",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_94",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(1)(c)  is  imposed  on  the  recipient;  or",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_95",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(d)  with the month in which the conferment of the Decoration",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_96",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "is  cancelled  or  annulled,",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_97",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "as  the  case  may  be.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_98",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(3)  if there is an appeal against such sentence or order referred \nto  in  paragraph  (1)(b)  or  (c)  by  the  recipient,  the  remembrance \nallowance shall not be paid commencing with the month in which \nsuch  sentence  or  order  is  confirmed  on  such  appeal.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_99",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(4)  if  the  recipient  receives  a  free  pardon  in  respect  of  such \nconviction  referred  to  in  paragraph  (1)(b),  or  if  the  cancelled  or \nannulled Decoration is restored to him, the remembrance allowance \nshall  be  restored  to  him  commencing  with  the  month  in  which \nthe  free  pardon  is  received  or  the  Decoration  is  restored.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_100",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(5)  Paragraph  (1)(c)  does  not  apply  to  a  recipient  where  the \ncourt  order  against  him  was  made  in  his  capacity  as  a  social \nguarantor.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_101",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "8",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_102",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Laws  of  Malaysia",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_103",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Act  744",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_104",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Grant to next-of-kin of recipient where decoration is conferred \nposthumously",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_105",
      "heading": "5.  Where  the  Decoration  is  conferred  posthumously  after  the \ncommencement of this Act, there may be made a grant of a total \nsum  of  ten  thousand  ringgit  once  only—",
      "content": "5.  Where  the  Decoration  is  conferred  posthumously  after  the \ncommencement of this Act, there may be made a grant of a total \nsum  of  ten  thousand  ringgit  once  only—",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_106",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(a)  to  the  spouse  or  spouses  and  children  of  the  deceased \nrecipient  who  are  living  on  the  date  of  the  conferment \nof  the  Decoration;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_107",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(b)  if  on  the  date  of  the  conferment  of  the  Decoration  no \nspouse  or  child  of  the  deceased  recipient  is  living,  to \nthe  parents  or  parent  of  the  deceased  recipient  who  are \nor  is  living  on  such  date;  or",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_108",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(c)  if  on  the  date  of  the  conferment  of  the  Decoration  no \nspouse,  child  or  parent  of  the  deceased  recipient  is \nliving, to the grandparents or grandparent of the deceased \nrecipient  who  are  or  is  living  on  such  date.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_109",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Prime  Minister  to  apportion  amount  to  be  paid",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_110",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "6.    The  amount  to  be  paid  to  the  spouse  or  spouses,  children, \nparents  or  grandparents,  as  the  case  may  be,  under  section  5 \nshall  be  in  such  proportions  as  may  be  determined  by  the  Prime \nMinister.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_111",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Remembrance allowance and sum to be charged to the Federal \nConsolidated  Fund",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_112",
      "heading": "7.  The  remembrance  allowance  and  sum  granted  under  this Act \nshall  be  charged  to  the  Federal  consolidated  Fund.",
      "content": "7.  The  remembrance  allowance  and  sum  granted  under  this Act \nshall  be  charged  to  the  Federal  consolidated  Fund.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_113",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Remembrance  allowance  and  sum  not  assignable,  etc.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_114",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "8.  Any  remembrance  allowance  or  sum  granted  under  this \nAct  shall  not  be  assignable,  transferable,  liable  to  be  attached, \nsequestrated  or  levied  upon  in  respect  of  any  claim.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
